    "content": "The correct order of basicity of the following compounds is <br><br><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m5aje85x/ab64fdeb-0b73-421f-82e4-be0ed346f98f/2c137050-c666-11ef-8e67-53e39b5d6286/file-jaoe38c1m5aje85y.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m5aje85x/ab64fdeb-0b73-421f-82e4-be0ed346f98f/2c137050-c666-11ef-8e67-53e39b5d6286/file-jaoe38c1m5aje85y.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"WB JEE 2016 Chemistry - General Organic Chemistry Question 15 English\">",
